These map was created by [GHOST]ThE kInG oF dOgS.

There is now two maps in this package (download one  get one free)
the new one is a retexture so it's more 'toony' now, i have also added windows and removed the lasers from around the bridge 

This is a very good map, recomended to everyone who likes awp and wants a "challange", the fog makes it harder to aim and makes more camping spots for campers hidden rooms with deagles in and stairs for those who like to go up a level.
